What makes a Punk Bird?¶

MVP: Minimum Viable Punk

  • Punches Above Weight Class
  • Wonton disregard for the Rules of Evolution

Nice-to-haves:

  • Gives exactly ZERO F's / Interolerable Cruelty
  • Goes after people

Stretch goal:

  • Murder?

10. American Dipper aka Water Ouzel¶

Dippers are Passerines, also known as perching birds, that have evolved a very non-perching bird approach to life. In the Dipper's case though, their adaptation is that they dive in fast moving streams to pick up their prey, aquatic insects. Daaayummmm.¶

9. The Shrike¶

Shrikes, like Dippers, are Passerines (perching birds). Shrikes, however, have evolved to become something very not songbird-like, they are PREDATORS, feasting on everything from grasshoppers on up to birds and even mice. FURTHER, they impale their prey on thorns and barbed wire. You know, to save them for later. Total punks.¶

5 (tie). Brown-headed Cowbird and Common Cuckoo¶

Cowbirds and Cuckoos are brood parasites, meaning they dump their eggs in other bird species nests and let them raise them instead. The young are much large than the actual offspring of the nesting birds, and they readily either kill or outcompete those young and then get reared by the "adoptive" parents. Just look at this photo!¶

3. Megapode¶

Megapodes or Brush Turkeys lay their eggs and then cover them with a giant pile of dirt and brush. Rather than incubate in the classic style, they have some kind of sixth sense that allows them to add and remove organic matter from the pile to regulate the temperature of the eggs. They do this faithfully during the entire incubation phase until hearing the peeps of the about-to-hatch turkey poults. Then they literally just walk away. The poults hatch from the eggs, dig themselves out, and they're on their own. SO PUNK.¶

1. Lammergeier¶

Lammergeiers or Bearded Vultures eat bones. That's it, just bones. Not the flesh off the bones. Bones. They drop e.g. goat femurs from high heights in the Ethiopian mountains, shattering them on the rocks below, then picking up (still large) bone bits and swallowing them whole. They have evolved special digestive juices so acidic they dissolve the bone quickly, making for a nutritious meal of BONES. Also they paint themselves with red mud to make themselves look more badass. As if this were necessary.¶
